#: ../../source/instances.rst:5
msgid "Managing Capacity With Instances"
msgstr "인스턴스로 용량 관리"

#: ../../source/instances.rst:13
msgid "Scaling your mesh is only available on Openshift deployments of |aap| and is possible through adding or removing nodes from your cluster dynamically, through the **Instances** resource of the |at| User Interface, without running the installation script."
msgstr "메시 확장은 |aap| 의 Openshift 배포에서만 사용할 수 있으며 설치 스크립트를 실행하지 않고도 |at| 사용자 인터페이스의 **인스턴스** 리소스를 통해 동적으로 클러스터에서 노드를 추가하거나 제거할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/instances.rst:16
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "사전 요구 사항"

#: ../../source/instances.rst:18
msgid "Be sure you have the minimum requirements for the RHEL virtual machine before proceeding. Refer to `Red Hat Ansible Automation Platform system requirements <https://access.redhat.com/documentation/en-us/red_hat_ansible_automation_platform/2.2/html/red_hat_ansible_automation_platform_installation_guide/planning-installation#red_hat_ansible_automation_platform_system_requirements>`_ for details."
msgstr "진행하기 전에 RHEL 가상 머신에 대한 최소 요구 사항이 있는지 확인하십시오. 자세한 내용은 `Red Hat Ansible Automation Platform system requirements <https://access.redhat.com/documentation/en-us/red_hat_ansible_automation_platform/2.2/html/red_hat_ansible_automation_platform_installation_guide/planning-installation#red_hat_ansible_automation_platform_system_requirements>`_에서 참조하십시오."

#: ../../source/instances.rst:20
msgid "RHEL nodes must properly be subscribed to:"
msgstr "RHEL 노드를 다음과 같이 올바르게 서브스크립션해야 합니다."

#: ../../source/instances.rst:22
msgid "RHEL subscription and with **baseos** and **appstream** repositories enabled"
msgstr "RHEL 서브스크립션 및 **baseos** 및 **appstream** 리포지토리가 활성화된 경우"

#: ../../source/instances.rst:23
msgid "|AAP| subscription and the proper |AAP| channel enabled:"
msgstr "|AAP| 서브스크립션 및 적절한 |AAP| 채널이 활성화되었습니다."

